<h1 id="welcomePageHeading">AddressMe</h1>

<p id="welcomeDescription">
  AddressMe is an online directory of all local businesses. This is a directory that can be added to, edited, or removed by any user. 
  AddressMe helps individuals that are new to the area by helping them learn what kind of businesses exist near them. This also helps local businesses get their name out there and helps advertise their business to all people in the town.
  Users can leave reviews about any businesses as well. Welcome to AddressMe!
</p>

<div id="welcomeLink">
  <%= link_to 'AddressMe', controller: 'addresses' %>
</div>
